data.name: XSheetPageBreak
desc: provides access to page breaks in a sheet.

methods.name: getColumnPageBreaks
desc: returns a sequence of descriptions of all horizontal page breaks on the sheet.
This includes manual and automatic page breaks. To add or remove manual breaks, use the com.sun.star.table.TableColumn.IsStartOfNewPage property of the column.

methods.name: getRowPageBreaks
desc: returns a sequence of descriptions of all vertical page breaks on the sheet.
This includes manual and automatic page breaks. To add or remove manual breaks, use the com.sun.star.table.TableRow.IsStartOfNewPage property of the row.

methods.name: removeAllManualPageBreaks
desc: removes all manual page breaks on the sheet.
